">Trần Đào</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%E1%BB%8B-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-1_IG0V5OLF6j9ToT33eDWg">Vị hữu - 為有</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BB%91/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n/poem-t4_fiBWUm1reYv0GgqhUGg">Vương Chiêu Quân - 王昭君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BB%91/author-RmmfVoamdwhG77VOgdRDUQ">Trương Trọng Tố</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n-ca/poem-FZsX7_qZDzP98yT1BN2IFA">Vương Chiêu Quân ca - 王昭君歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-tOqeEdGQ0OZRwfU1Vi35GA">Lưu Trường Khanh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
